<para style="p">For the chief musician; on stringed instruments, set to the Sheminith style. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, do not rebuke me in your anger</para>

<para style="q1">or discipline me in your wrath.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Have mercy on me, Yahweh, for I am frail;</para>

<para style="q1">heal me, Yahweh, for my bones are shaking.</para>
